                                        web applications are fast, secure, and capable of handling complex data workflows.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            @*End Service Item*@

                            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                                <div class="icon flex-shrink-0"><i class="bi bi-binoculars"></i></div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="title stretched-link" id="service_title4">
                                        Database Design
                                        & Integration
                                    </h4>
                                    <p class="description" id="service_description4">
