                                        procedures, normalization, and secure data handling for smooth integration with
                                        applications.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            @*End Service Item*@

                            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
                                <div class="icon flex-shrink-0"><i class="bi bi-brightness-high"></i></div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="title stretched-link" id="service_title5">
                                        API Development
                                        & Integration
                                    </h4>
                                    <p class="description" id="service_description5">
                                        Building and integrating RESTful APIs to connect different systems and platforms,
                                        enabling smooth data exchange and automation between web and mobile applications.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            @*End Service Item*@

                            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 service-item d-flex" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
                                <div class="icon flex-shrink-0"><i class="bi bi-calendar4-week"></i></div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="title stretched-link" id="service_title6">
                                        Website Maintenance
                                        & Support
                                    </h4>
                                    <p class="description" id="service_description6">
                                        Providing regular updates, bug fixes, performance optimization, and feature enhancements
                                        to keep your website secure, updated, and running flawlessly.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            @*End Service Item*@

                        </div>

                    </div>

